fine art and jewellery collections.
Sun Alliance and Chubb own 9 per cent of each other's equity capital. Sun
Alliance also reinsures (via a quota share treaty) 10 per cent of Chubb's
specialty lines and 15.75 per cent of its standard lines business.
Chubb has been one of the most consistently profitable US insurers.
