<HEADLINE>
FT  01 OCT 92 / TV researcher remanded on bail
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
MR Ben Hamilton, a television researcher involved in a Channel 4 documentary
alleging collusion between the Royal Ulster Constabulary and loyalist
paramilitaries in Northern Ireland, was yesterday remanded on bail on a
charge of perjury.
He appeared before Horsferry Road Magistrates in central London.
</TEXT>
